article_id:1609,category_name:News,title_name:Announcing Gala Dragalia!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia will start at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601186400"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>What are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?</div><div>・The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons will be boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Note: Every Gala Dragalia adventurer and dragon added in past Gala Dragalia summon showcases may appear in this summon showcase. For information about which adventurers and dragons may appear, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Appearance Rates and check the Appearance Rates section.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601186400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1601445599"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the 5★ adventurers appearing in this Gala Draglia below.</div><div><br></div><div>5★adventurers:</div><div>
